subSubSection.paragraph:
Metasoma.
Mat. First metasomal segment (
Fig. 10H
) round in cross-section of basal 0.3, dorso-lateral carina and lateral groove present. First tergite 3.2× longer than width of postpetiole. Second tergite 0.86× as long as first tergite, 1.8× longer than its apical width; thyridium oval, its distance from basal margin of tergite 3.5× its diameter. Third tergite 1.3× longer than its apical width. Sixth and seventh tergites with emarginations medially. Ovipositor sheath approx. 1.6× longer than hind femur, ovipositor (
Fig. 10D
) gradually upcurved.
